{"id":1848,"date":"2022-09-27T21:07:44","date_gmt":"2022-09-27T19:07:44","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/connecta.no\/?page_id=1848"},"modified":"2026-02-03T15:16:04","modified_gmt":"2026-02-03T14:16:04","slug":"tjenester","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/connecta.no\/tjenester\/","title":{"rendered":"Tjenester"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-page\" data-elementor-id=\"1848\" class=\"elementor elementor-1848\" data-elementor-post-type=\"page\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-be9fe0b elementor-section-height-min-height elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-items-middle\" data-id=\"be9fe0b\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-background-overlay\"><\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-16b36a1\" data-id=\"16b36a1\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-548d460 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"548d460\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Tjenester<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bb2b31a elementor-widget-divider--view-line elementor-widget elementor-widget-divider\" data-id=\"bb2b31a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"divider.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-divider\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-divider-separator\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-bd2bba7 elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"bd2bba7\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-64b8b8a\" data-id=\"64b8b8a\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d2fd20f elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"d2fd20f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bf400ba elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bf400ba\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Individualterapi<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-547f05b elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"547f05b\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Livet kan by p\u00e5 mange utfordringer. Som oftest greier vi \u00e5 takle utfordringene selv med hjelp fra de rundt oss, men noen ganger\u00a0kan livet oppleves som s\u00e5 vanskelig at det\u00a0er behov for \u00e5 snakke med en utenforst\u00e5ende fagperson som kan hjelpe\u00a0med \u00e5 finne\u00a0l\u00f8sninger og veien videre.\u00a0<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Da kan det v\u00e6re nyttig \u00e5 f\u00e5 hjelp fra en profesjonell som kan gi deg innspill, innsikt og verkt\u00f8y for\u00a0hvordan g\u00e5 videre s\u00e5 du ikke blir begrenset av problemene dine.\u00a0Bakgrunnen for \u00e5 komme til samtale hos oss kan v\u00e6re et \u00f8nske\u00a0om selvutvikling, opplevelse av tristhet, angst symptomer,\u00a0bekymringer,\u00a0f\u00f8lelsen av og ikke strekke til, vonde tanker og f\u00f8lelser og mange andre\u00a0ting.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-c436d1b elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"c436d1b\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b0bf7e6\" data-id=\"b0bf7e6\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db27b95 elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"db27b95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8cae9dc elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8cae9dc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Onlineterapi<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-314f0ba elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"314f0ba\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-d07f0f8\" data-id=\"d07f0f8\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e564a25 elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e564a25\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>I dagens samfunn har det blitt stadig mer vanlig \u00e5 gjennomf\u00f8re m\u00f8ter online, og dette gjelder ogs\u00e5 for terapi. En stor fordel med onlineterapi er\u00a0at man sparer tid p\u00e5 reise, parkeringsutgifter, og at man st\u00e5r fritt til \u00e5 velge fagperson uavhengig av geografisk tilh\u00f8righet.\u00a0<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Man kan delta fra hvor\u00a0som helst i verden, noe som tilbyr fleksibilitet i en travel hverdag. Online terapi kan v\u00e6re like effektivt som tradisjonell terapi med personlig<br \/>oppm\u00f8te. For \u00e5 sikre en best mulig opplevelse, er det imidlertid noen forberedelser som kan v\u00e6re nyttige:<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-bb51020\" data-id=\"bb51020\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa00124 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"aa00124\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"5078\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/connecta.no\/nick-morrison-fhnnjk1yj7y-unsplash\/\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C480&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"640,480\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C480&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"640\" height=\"480\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C480&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5078\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1 640w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?resize=300%2C225&amp;ssl=1 300w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?resize=600%2C450&amp;ssl=1 600w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?resize=400%2C300&amp;ssl=1 400w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?resize=200%2C150&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-attachment-id=\"5078\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/connecta.no\/nick-morrison-fhnnjk1yj7y-unsplash\/\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C480&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"640,480\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/nick-morrison-FHnnjk1Yj7Y-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C480&amp;ssl=1\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2d050d5 elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2d050d5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Fin<\/strong><b>n et passende sted og tidspunkt<br \/><\/b><\/p><ul><li>Velg et stille og privat sted for terapitimen. Det er viktig \u00e5 finne et sted hvor andre ikke kan h\u00f8re det som snakkes om i\u00a0timene. Taushetsplikten er like viktig online som ved fysisk oppm\u00f8te. Offentlige steder som kafeer eller parker passer derfor\u00a0ikke for terapisamtaler.<\/li><li>Velg et tidspunkt hvor du ikke vil bli forstyrret, og n\u00e5r du f\u00f8ler deg relativt uthvilt og oppmerksom.<\/li><li>Velg komfortable omgivelser. En behagelig stol, tilstrekkelig belysning og en ordnet bakgrunn kan bidra til en mer behagelig samtale.<\/li><\/ul><div><div><b>Forbered deg mentalt<\/b><\/div><div><ul><li>Forberedelse: Det kan v\u00e6re hjelpsomt \u00e5 reflektere over hva du \u00f8nsker \u00e5 diskutere under terapitimen. \u00c5 lage noen notater p\u00e5 forh\u00e5nd kan forhindre at du glemmer viktige punkter under samtalen.<\/li><li>Sett av tid etterp\u00e5: Terapi kan v\u00e6re energikrevende, s\u00e5 det er best om timen ikke blir presset inn mellom mange andre planer. Ikke planlegg for mange aktiviteter rett etter timen slik at du gir deg selv tid til \u00e5 bearbeide og reflektere rundt samtalen.<\/li><li>Fokuser p\u00e5 terapisamtalen: Unng\u00e5 \u00e5 multitaske under terapitimen. N\u00e5r vi har terapi online kan vi noen ganger glemme at terapi krever mye oppmerksomhet, og vi begynner \u00e5 gj\u00f8re andre ting mens vi lytter til det terapeuten sier. For at terapien skal ha best effekt, er det viktig at vi har oppmerksomheten rettet kun mot det vi snakker om i terapien.<\/li><\/ul><div><div><b>Teknisk oppsett<\/b><\/div><div><ul><li>Sjekk utstyret ditt: Forsikre deg om at enheten din fungerer optimalt. Test mikrofon, h\u00f8yttalere eller hodetelefoner, samt kamera, for \u00e5 sikre god lyd- og bildekvalitet. En st\u00f8rre skjerm som p\u00e5 en datamaskin eller et nettbrett anbefales for en bedre opplevelse.<\/li><li>Stabil internettforbindelse: En p\u00e5litelig internettforbindelse er viktig for \u00e5 unng\u00e5 avbrudd.<\/li><li>Bli kjent med plattformen: Terapien skjer via en bestemt plattform som krever opprettelse av en konto og innlogging. Pr\u00f8v \u00e5 logge inn litt f\u00f8r timen starter, spesielt ved f\u00f8rste time, for \u00e5 gj\u00f8re deg kjent med hvordan plattformen fungerer.\u00a0<\/li><\/ul><\/div><div>Alle terapitimer foreg\u00e5r gjennom en sikker plattform som overholder europeiske personvernregler (GDPR), og det kreves derfor innlogging f\u00f8r\u00a0<span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-secondary ); font-size: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-size ); font-weight: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-weight );\">hver time.<\/span><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-d12ad3a elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"d12ad3a\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-b89474e\" data-id=\"b89474e\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-08b85cc elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"08b85cc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da02b8d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"da02b8d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Familieveiledning<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1fe0ca2 elementor-hidden-mobile elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1fe0ca2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-canvas-width=\"550.9759999999998\"><div data-canvas-width=\"600.6879999999996\"><div data-canvas-width=\"600.6879999999996\">De fleste foreldre opplever perioder hvor de f\u00f8ler seg r\u00e5dville og fortvilet\u00a0i forhold til hvordan forst\u00e5 eller ivareta barnet \/ ungdommen sin. Det er f\u00e5\u00a0ting som er mer s\u00e5rbart for oss enn barna v\u00e5re, og det \u00a0er derfor ekstra\u00a0vondt n\u00e5r vi bekymrer oss eller opplever at forholdet til\u00a0barnet \/ ungdommen v\u00e5r blir vanskelig eller konfliktfylt. Bekymringene\u00a0kan ofte v\u00e6re flere og sammensatte, og utfordringene vil kunne variere\u00a0med barnets alder.\u00a0<\/div><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-inner-section elementor-element elementor-element-5366bbf elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"5366bbf\" data-element_type=\"section\" data-e-type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-no\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-0f130a2\" data-id=\"0f130a2\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8525d0a elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8525d0a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" data-attachment-id=\"5077\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/connecta.no\/luana-azevedo-2x0set_osh8-unsplash\/\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C960&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"640,960\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C960&amp;ssl=1\" width=\"640\" height=\"960\" src=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C960&amp;ssl=1\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-5077\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash.jpg?w=640&amp;ssl=1 640w, https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash.jpg?resize=200%2C300&amp;ssl=1 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" data-attachment-id=\"5077\" data-permalink=\"https:\/\/connecta.no\/luana-azevedo-2x0set_osh8-unsplash\/\" data-orig-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C960&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"640,960\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash\" data-image-description=\"\" data-image-caption=\"\" data-large-file=\"https:\/\/i0.wp.com\/connecta.no\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/04\/luana-azevedo-2X0Set_oSh8-unsplash.jpg?fit=640%2C960&amp;ssl=1\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-inner-column elementor-element elementor-element-ed8d38d\" data-id=\"ed8d38d\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b4367e9 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b4367e9\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div data-canvas-width=\"600.6879999999996\">Foreldreveiledning kan v\u00e6re for deg som er bekymret for barnets trivsel eller utvikling, som opplever at kommunikasjonen og relasjonen til barnet ditt har kommet inn i et negativt spor, eller for deg som opplever usikkerhet i fht hvilke rammer og grenser barnet ditt trenger.<\/div><div data-canvas-width=\"600.6879999999996\"><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-2c37380 );\">\u00a0<\/span><\/div><div data-canvas-width=\"430.94399999999985\">Vi har sv\u00e6rt god kompetanse p\u00e5 barn og ungdoms utviklingstrinn og har lang erfaring i \u00e5 veilede foreldre som p\u00e5 en eller annen m\u00e5te trenger hjelp og st\u00f8tte i foreldrerollen.<\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-136e6d1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"136e6d1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>I forbindelse med samlivsbrudd kan\u00a0det oppst\u00e5 uenighet og konflikter\u00a0mellom de voksne knyttet til samarbeid rundt barna.\u00a0Vi kan veilede foreldre i hvordan kommunisere og samarbeide om l\u00f8sninger rundt barna slik at barna ikke beh\u00f8ver \u00e5\u00a0leve i et vedvarende konflikt-felt mellom de to voksne som betyr\u00a0mest for dem.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ab77d05 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ab77d05\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"font-style: inherit; font-weight: inherit;\">Den moderne familie kan best\u00e5 av b\u00e5de mine, dine og felles barn. Det inneb\u00e6rer at man m\u00e5 forholde seg til partnerens barn fra tidligere forhold og samarbeidet partneren har med sin ex, og \/ eller omvendt. Det kan oppleves vanskelig \u00e5 navigere i et slikt landskap, og mange opplever at dette gir grobunn for konflikter b\u00e5de mellom de voksne, og mellom barna og de voksne i familien. Da kan det v\u00e6re nyttig \u00e5 f\u00e5 et utenforst\u00e5ende blikk som kan bist\u00e5 med kart og kompass i et utfordrende terreng.\u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f0285ee elementor-widget elementor-widget-spacer\" data-id=\"f0285ee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"spacer.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-spacer-inner\"><\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Tjenester Individualterapi Livet kan by p\u00e5 mange utfordringer. Som oftest greier vi \u00e5 takle utfordringene selv med hjelp fra de rundt oss, men noen ganger\u00a0kan livet oppleves som s\u00e5 vanskelig at det\u00a0er behov for \u00e5 snakke med en utenforst\u00e5ende fagperson som kan hjelpe\u00a0med \u00e5 finne\u00a0l\u00f8sninger og veien videre.\u00a0 \u00a0 Da kan det v\u00e6re nyttig \u00e5 [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":223811887,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"no-sidebar","site-content-layout":"page-builder","ast-site-content-layout":"","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"disabled","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"","ast-featured-img":"disabled","footer-sml-layout":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-sti